# OS Upgrade Tools
# These tools are defined inline in the agent DSL files.
# This file serves as a tool registry reference for the v2 export format.

# Tools:
#   get_upgrade_candidates — Identify sites eligible for OS upgrade
#   create_upgrade_plan — Create a phased upgrade plan with rollback criteria
#   execute_upgrade_batch — Execute an upgrade batch within a plan
#   verify_upgrade_health — Run post-upgrade health verification on a site
#   rollback_upgrade — Rollback a site to previous OS version
